    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, appearing exactly as it did when it first left the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, mirror-like shine without a single stone chip, scratch, or swirl mark. Inside, the cabin remains in factory-new condition, with the leather seats still firm and the interior trim completely free of wear. Mechanically, it performs perfectly, having been stored in a climate-controlled environment and maintained with obsessive care. This is a rare opportunity to own a truly pristine example that looks and drives like a brand-new car.",
      "price": 49500.0,
