    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to a standard that can only be described as flawless. Every aspect of this motorcar, from the lustrous finish of the exterior to the immaculate detailing of the cabin, remains in showroom condition. Mechanically, the vehicle performs with the precision and refinement expected of a premier acquisition. This is an invitation for the discerning collector to secure a specimen of rare caliber and peerless preservation.",
      "price": 48500.0,
