      "description": "We are pleased to present this exemplary vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This unit remains in pristine, showroom condition, reflecting a level of care that is increasingly rare in the pre-owned market. Every component has been meticulously inspected to ensure it meets our rigorous criteria for mechanical and aesthetic perfection. For the discerning driver who demands nothing less than the absolute best, this offering represents a premier investment in both performance and prestige.",
      "price": 48500.0,
